<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Admin Rights Have Been Granted to You</h1>
    <p>
      <%= link_to user_url(@current_user), user_url(@current_user) %> has given you admin rights on GPEN to the organization entitled <%= link_to @organization.name, organization_url(@organization) %>. Your admin rights will expire on <b><%= @end_date.to_formatted_s(:long) %></b></p>

    <p>Please let <%= link_to user_url(@current_user), user_url(@current_user) %> (CC'ed) know if this was a mistake.</p>

    <p>
      All the Best,<br>
      The GPEN Team
    </p>
    
  </body>
</html>